{"tid":946852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恆安邨單位疑燒炭釀火警 27歲男及5隻貓死亡","createTime":"2018-12-18T23:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T05:25:52.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"f955560a573f7cf4ef4c3319e474d0a8e049c5ef","tid":946852,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T23:44:11.000Z","msg":"【07:25】消防發現有5隻貓屍，由愛協人員撿走<br />\n【06：40】消防發現房間有炭爐及遺書<br />\n【06:20】男子送院搶救不治<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山恆安邨恆峰樓，凌晨4時44分，8樓一個單位發生火警，冒出濃煙，街坊發現報警，約100多人自行疏散到地下。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場開喉灌救，約半小時將火救熄，並在單位內救出一名27歲男子，他口臉熏黑，懷疑吸入濃煙昏迷，送威爾斯醫院惜搶救不治。另有兩名男女住客亦吸入濃煙不適，清醒送院。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，火警單位面積5米乘8米，住有一家七口，以及一名女兒的男友。起火房間面積2米乘2米，消防發現單位內有炭爐及遺書，相信死者是女兒的男友，懷疑有人燒炭導致火警。消防亦發現單位有5隻貓屍，由愛護動物協會人員撿走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181219/59046241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046241&d=RTl5t2WQ9K2ZqvlqU6Ob9jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7cbba154\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F59046241&h=f9be5796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181219/59046241</a>"},{"pid":"0dfca489d6d38d98a000b843273974f24af50118","tid":946852,"uid":35420,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T23:45:39.000Z","msg":"係人地屋企燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59d3d52e92827252e2b868bf58fe2ab6ef3dafa","tid":946852,"uid":40470,"like":42,"dislike":7,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T23:47:37.000Z","msg":"窮鬼學人養咁多貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812b9fa012849584e46348be80cd7067206a0cf","tid":946852,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dfca489d6d38d98a000b843273974f24af50118","tid":946852,"uid":35420,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"cit